{"tid":2203659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"可以強姦但不容攪基！印度中央政府反對同婚 理由是社會價值觀","createTime":"2020-09-15T13:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T23:34:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6b5d7946abd9758cac0f7447f6c9dc7ddaba743d","tid":2203659,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009150145.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009150145.aspx&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=8ae2946b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009150145.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"0484c089db53963a73cef6a47263c8983a2ea947","tid":2203659,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"台灣可以同婚，內地不行"},{"pid":"b90daeb151a352f99fc404b53345abc07a1a9c65","tid":2203659,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"（中央社記者康世人新德里15日專電）印度同志等社群正在爭取同性婚姻合法化，但由右翼保守印度人民黨主導的印度中央政府昨天在德里高等法院，以不符合社會價值觀為由，反對同性婚姻合法化。<br />\n<br />\n印度最高法院2018年9月6日裁定刑法第377條處罰同性成人間合意的非自然性行為違憲後，印度150多年的非自然性行為刑罰終於除罪化。印度同性戀、雙性戀和跨性別（LGBT）社群繼續向法院爭取讓同性婚姻合法化，德里高等法院昨天開庭審理。<br />\n<br />\n綜合印度人報（The Hindu）等印度媒體今天報導，代表印度中央政府的總檢察長梅塔（Tushar Mehta）昨天在法庭上聲稱，「我們的法律制度、社會和價值觀不認同同性間的婚姻」。<br />\n<br />\n梅塔說，最高法院憲法法庭2018年的裁決，只是廢除同性性行為的刑事罪責。<br />\n<br />\n德里高等法院首席法官巴特爾（D N Patel）和法官賈蘭（Prateek Jalan）表示，法院正在考慮這項（同婚合法化）公益訴訟是否應該進行，「今天的世界正在改變中，這些變化可能適用於我們國家（印度），也可能不適用」。<br />\n<br />\n法官也詢問提出公益訴訟者是否在申請登記同性婚姻時遇到困難。<br />\n<br />\n這起公益訴訟主要由印度LGBT社群團體成員密特拉（Abhijit Iyer Mitra）提出；另有3人根據「1995年印度教婚姻法」（Hindu Marriage Act of 1995）第5條訴請承認同性婚姻，他們所持理由是「法條並未區分同性或異性婚姻」。"},{"pid":"e4b742ffca613c6f28611c9fb1a59321bac6877c","tid":2203659,"uid":121784,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"好明顯, 印度中央政府, 對印度傳統文化一知半解<br />\n<br />\n印度教主神Shiva係雌雄同體<br />\n印度教火神Agni係雙性戀既, 會接受其他神奉獻的精液"},{"pid":"2eb4e5daa444c01b56a895724671e230f49a5baa","tid":2203659,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e316735e0236d04990a24a14d54cb3b31d95c7a","tid":2203659,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b5d7946abd9758cac0f7447f6c9dc7ddaba743d","tid":2203659,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009150145.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009150145.aspx&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=8ae2946b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009150145.aspx</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"所以連登仔唔會去民主大國印度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74add1af9071ac7a2da60d9dc4e372d0e426b741","tid":2203659,"uid":323740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:18:09.000Z","msg":"咖哩屎棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38acf29389c4644b97faa04a7269fc3fe0468dc4","tid":2203659,"uid":238370,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4b742ffca613c6f28611c9fb1a59321bac6877c","tid":2203659,"uid":121784,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:30:18.000Z","msg":"好明顯, 印度中央政府, 對印度傳統文化一知半解<br />\n<br />\n印度教主神Shiva係雌雄同體<br />\n印度教火神Agni係雙性戀既, 會接受其他神奉獻的精液"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T23:26:08.000Z","msg":"印度傳統社會對LGBT本黎好寬容，係英治之後引入套耶撚保守入黎搞到印度對LGBT冇咁容忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cc3c87a1237c8a4c1a4dd4722ae674c5535f2f","tid":2203659,"uid":124663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-